Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a spooky chateau on 3rd street, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that abandoned house that no one lives in anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, I heard my mom say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some strange man came out of nowhere and started living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it looks so spooky, no one wants to go near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems we need to scout out that house, like the police would.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our duty as the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hidden in the famous painter's masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this astonishing mystery you think you can see but can't!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really strange to think someone would\Npurposely move into that kind of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say, I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually more interested in the one residing in your\Nhouse, rather than whoever's in this haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Okiya Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he's a Holmes fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're choosing to be illogical, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can lend my house to whoever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's become really pretty here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the one who moved in took good care of the landscape, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, you're giving me a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We agreed it was only valid until today, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two or three more days won't hurt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we have our own schedules!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I can only give you until tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have my own concerns here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had better keep your promise, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Mortgage Company...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with your nameplate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true—there's no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't placed a name on it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think you wouldn't put your own nameplate, it sure is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could he be up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a house...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy died!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he wasn't in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He collapsed at home last night and managed\Nto call for an ambulance himself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he was acting strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what he was planning to do\Nafter moving into that haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our minds won't be at ease, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With an unsolved mystery lingering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The neighbors said they don't know much about that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he moved in three months before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't acquaint himself with the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seldom left the house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone said he would always either stay inside to\Nfix up the house or go out to maintain the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he didn't have a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here, it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you an acquaintance of the man who lived here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean, you all knew Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a sensei of some kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Wada Rokurou was a famous\NWestern-style painter representing Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that guy was a painter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you are too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:45.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:50.74,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yagami Keiichi (50)\NArt Dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:51.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm an art dealer that has been handling\NWada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s masterpieces for a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei said he borrowed this chateau to use as an\Nart studio for painting a new masterpiece, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:59.08,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hayashi Kaoru (25)\NYagami's Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,There's no time for that, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and find the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were to steal them, it would be tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like this was a mystery easily solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About who that person was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what he was doing here, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was painting all the time, it would make\Nsense as to why he didn't go out often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I wonder what kind of picture he was painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We really wanna see, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drop by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because it was only borrowed as an art studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this kid be that man from childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, children?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to see that guy's paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't find any, even after searching the other rooms and upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that someone stole them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, we didn't see any art supplies at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No easels, canvases, paint, or brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this really is his art studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The perfect chateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:35.55,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Wada Rokurou (55)\NWestern-style Painter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:36.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,At that place, I'll create a once-in-a-lifetime masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei absolutely said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't it be that he simply put his art\Nsupplies away after he finished painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's give it one more careful search!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to commence the deconstruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"What"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the guy who was arguing with Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was arguing with Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what did you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone has died and you feel lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, forgive me, my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:21.77,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shishikura Yasuo (31)\NBeika Mortgage Company Staff
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,See, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,With the Beika Mortgage Company, Shishikura is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our company purchased this land three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We decided to demolish this chateau for other use, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He requested to borrow the house from us for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we agreed to let him for just three months, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You "won't leave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something has come up and changed my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me two or three more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's causing us problems, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already sold this land to another customer,\Nand agreed to demolish this house immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just two or three more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really put me in a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's why those two were fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if he's no longer with us, that means the problem is gone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carry out the belongings and start the demolition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until we've located the painting Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} mentioned, can you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Shishikura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's help them find the painting as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sounds fun, like a treasure hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you're not going to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s final masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just think of the aesthetic value!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's futile, searching for that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Futile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where on earth did Sensei put his painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's strange as well—this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If painting had been done here, there\Nshould at least be a scent of paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't smell anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true—just like the boy says...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Sensei didn't paint anything here after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remaining mystery revolves around why he borrowed the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just too soft, you can't even firmly refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it looks like nothing came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no painting to begin with, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, we can get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's get this done quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking for Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We received a message from Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It will be complete today, so please come see the painting," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Come see the painting..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} actually said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four or five days ago, he mailed this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Due to the weather, it took longer than expected, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it will be complete by this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be sure to bring Auntie here to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-Rokurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Sensei's handwriting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,Addressed To Tohto Beika City, Beika Town 15-7 Kafuuen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Eguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's your name, isn't it, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's "Kafuuen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:14.67,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Eguchi Mina (24)\NPrivate Health Care Provider
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's a retirement home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's the place I work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A retirement home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you're Takatoo Saeko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's actually something I heard about from Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he often visited a chateau as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And an auntie of his always took care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.81,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Takatoo Saeko (71)\NWada's Aunt
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He said that auntie was now in a retirement home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was always taken care of by Sensei, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since Takatoo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s injury a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been suffering from amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even remember who she is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amnesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even still, Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would take\Ntime out of his busy schedule to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, dear auntie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm now working on a masterpiece that's just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How exciting is that, Takatoo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do bring it here when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be impossible to bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean it's a big project?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you feast your eyes on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think even you will regain your memories, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gate guarding your memories will swing right open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Sensei actually did work on his final piece in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and tear this house apart to make up for our lost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you couldn't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said you're giving me a hard time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Shishikura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't proceed if there are people inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have other construction sites to get to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't keep going with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go grab some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No point arguing with a wimp like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That good-for-nothing guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I thought we could finally get started...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Takatoo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we wait here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just stay and sit around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing was found in the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt he actually painted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lied to his favorite auntie who cared for him when he was little?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for working on a painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason did he have for borrowing this haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem we're back to the same mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for what he did, looks like he only fixed\Nthe house and took care of the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just ahead of this house, there's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kids finally went home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bright and sunny today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's walk our way to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was trying to dig a tunnel from that house to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tried to steal his way into the underground deposit vault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expected something like an underground tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the house to this bank, the direct distance is only about 50 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were to dig 60 centimeters per day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three months would be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He dug away during the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, during the day, he would bring up the dirt and deposit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By doing that, he could make it appear he was gardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about him fixing up the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Merely camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't look natural if he only worked on the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be impossible to bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were stealing billions of yen, it sure\Nwould be impossible to carry around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you feast your eyes on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think even you will regain your memories, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one out there who wouldn't be\Nshocked to feast their eyes on billions of yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was referring to shocking her out of her amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfect, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made my head spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's find the entrance to the tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kids... are back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that man went as far as to fight the mortgage\Ncompany staff in order to keep staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't go back in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the storage cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's not connected to the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he could have torn up some of the\Nwooden flooring and dug under there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go check if there's a void under the floor, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not in this room, it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's try elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, they sure are noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:31.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,At Aunt Saeko's House
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And stop making messes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"At Aunt Saeko's House"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, if I consider it like this, it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something strange has come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And because of it, we couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've gotta move to the next site.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what about the demolition of this house!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the fault of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, this house really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was where Auntie lived, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I might have, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a beautiful house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Auntie lost her husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She apparently had a pretty rough time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that, she was very wealthy and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Memories from the past when she was fortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to burn it down completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop doing foolish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if the fire were to spread to the rest of the neighborhood!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But please understand, I have my own duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's willing to wait one more day to tear down the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have just done it, and tore it down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the painting wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no underground tunnels...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the reason that man borrowed this house was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he could work on something for his auntie, Takatoo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A once-in-a-lifetime masterpiece made just for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei's masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still in progress, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be complete tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's bright and sunny... Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is entirely complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gorgeous sea of flowers flooding around the chateau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the masterpiece Wada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had worked toward for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this view!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the bad weather, it took extra time to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why he asked for more days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takatoo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Know this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers blooming around the garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And swaying in the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there was this chateau...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband stood beside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The always-cute Roku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, my nephew, often came over to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} lost his mother when he was still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He viewed me as his mother after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takatoo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gate to her memories opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why it had to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chateau that looks so much like her house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The nameplate was meant to be signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:22:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he couldn't place a nameplate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not until the flowers bloomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, as with any art project, you only put it on after it's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what a signature is for!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The haunted house, and the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a waste, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man's wish finally reached his auntie, so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just leave me here, you guys!
